    <item>
      <title>美国国防工业将在参议院乌克兰边境协议中获得 350 亿美元的收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/us-defense-industry-would-get-35-billion-boon-in-senate-ukraine-border-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防工业将从周日晚间公布的参议院妥协方案中获得约350亿美元，该妥协方案将为乌克兰提供数十亿美元的军事援助，并为以色列和太平洋盟友提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/us-defense-industry-would-get-35-billion-boon-in-senate-ukraine-border-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚人支持总理阿尔巴尼斯的税收赌博，但支持率没有增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/australians-back-pm-albanese-s-tax-gamble-but-no-bump-in-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞修改立法减税措施以提高中低收入者福利的计划受到好评，但这些变化并未转化为对中左翼政府潜在支持的增加。选举年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/australians-back-pm-albanese-s-tax-gamble-but-no-bump-in-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:07:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员就乌克兰援助和美国边境达成协议，但强硬的共和党人仍然是威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/senators-reach-deal-on-ukraine-aid-and-us-border-but-republicans-still-a-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，参议员们发布了一项两党协议，要求实施新的美国移民限制，并为乌克兰提供数十亿美元的援助，尽管这项措施在众议院面临很大的阻力，但这是至关重要的一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/senators-reach-deal-on-ukraine-aid-and-us-border-but-republicans-still-a-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国誓言对中东进行更多打击，同时试图避免更广泛的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/us-promises-more-mideast-strikes-while-trying-to-avert-wider-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在连续三天的惩罚性袭击之后，拜登政府誓言将对伊朗军队及其在中东的代理人进行更多打击，尽管高级官员坚称美国不会陷入长期的地区冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/us-promises-more-mideast-strikes-while-trying-to-avert-wider-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:19:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽伦斯基呼吁不仅在军事领域进行广泛的领导层变革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/zelenskiy-seeks-leadership-change-not-just-in-military-rai-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基表示，他正在考虑对乌克兰的领导层进行广泛的变革，而不仅仅是军事领域，同时也承认乌克兰为击退俄罗斯入侵而进行的战争努力已经陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/zelenskiy-seeks-leadership-change-not-just-in-military-rai-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 22:58:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
